race.comment: Tricky race to assess with many of these facing the starter for the first time. SWAGGERING (3) hit the frame at Gatton on debut before being given time to mature. Another to get some weight relief and has race experience over a lot of these. Among the leading chances. LUMINOUS GIRL (6) is another at the races for the first time but is sure to be well-educated from the Bruce barn. Keep safe. TENGUN JESSIE (9) has had two trials in preparation for this and looks set to run well. Betting will hold the key. MOROCCAN WIND (1) son of Tassort from Queen Cora on debut. At his most recent trial was out of the placings but makes debut on home track. Include.
